727693f-a.title: Queens: Prince Street - 35th Avenue
727693f-a.text:
Pringe Street, adjoining the N.W. corner of 35th Avenue,
showing the 109th Precinct of the New York City Police Depart-
ment. This was formerly a private mansion owned by the Winter
Estate in 1873 and by M.R. Shaffer in 1891.
P. L. Sperr  March 12, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
